metadata.name: Hope
metadata.description:
You wanna leave, but you can't.
Something or someone holds you there.
You know there isn't any chance here,
but you can't leave...
or maybe
Nothing there, no one holds you,
but you still have hope, a false hope...
or maybe
You're waiting for someone,
to save you from this,
"Corrupted demon land"
You wanna leave...
You know there isn't any chance.
